data.description: This beautiful home offers 3 spacious bedrooms and 1 ½ baths. The main bedroom has an impressive walk-in closet. The eat-in kitchen is large with ample counterspace and cabinets. There's plenty of original charm in this home including hardwood floors, wide staircases, and wood beams. The finished attic is a versatile bonus room offering many different options for use. Outside, you can sip a cup of coffee on the deck while enjoying the fenced in yard with vinyl fencing. The rear parking space is located close to the back door, making it easier to carry in groceries. Additional features include vinyl windows, a new boiler in 2020, 150 amperage and the architectural roof is approximately 15 years.
